00:01:11.546 --> 00:01:16.946
Waht are you going to make?
Rice Crackers

00:01:24.077 --> 00:01:27.773
Ingredients required to make Rice Crackers

00:01:28.094 --> 00:01:37.728
Rice Flour, Chopped Onions, Green Chilli, Bengal Gram,
 Cumin Seeds, Salt, Curry Leaves &amp; Oil

00:01:58.714 --> 00:02:02.611
Take a pan and heat some oil in it

00:02:13.428 --> 00:02:41.237
Take a bowl of rice flour and add soaked bengal gram, chopped onions,
 green chillies, cumin seeds, salt &amp; curry leaves and add water to make a dough

00:02:47.531 --> 00:02:53.067
Make small flat patties with the dough

00:02:58.382 --> 00:03:06.053
Fry the patties

00:05:32.765 --> 00:05:38.937
Take them in a serving plate

00:06:48.496 --> 00:06:54.220
It's soft and crispy!

